data.description: You will love this immaculate 1 story home with quick access to Beltway 8, Westpark Toll, Chinatown, Vietnamese town and surrounded by many restaurants, bars and shopping centers. This house boasts a beautiful tiles and spacious living room space which are perfect for entertaining and gathering. This home is also situated in the corner  lot which offers a larger common area and extra parking spaces outside the unit. Fridge, and washer are INCLUDED! Tenant currently under lease until March 2024 with monthly rent of $1400/month. Tenant has been there for more than 4 years and expect rent raise for the next renewal cycle. Low tax rate and well maintained house. Low price point that's good for both investment and primary living. Look no further.
